	<h2 class="story">
		

		

		
		

		

		

		

		<span id="title-172724375" class="story-title"> <a   href="//tech.slashdot.org/story/24/01/11/1958253/hertz-is-selling-20000-electric-vehicles-to-buy-gasoline-cars-instead">Hertz is Selling 20,000 Electric Vehicles To Buy Gasoline Cars Instead</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://edition.cnn.com/2024/01/11/business/hertz-tesla-selling/index.html"  title="External link - https://edition.cnn.com/2024/01/11/business/hertz-tesla-selling/index.html" target="_blank"> (cnn.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
